ygData.messageBody:
Last night on Karana I was playing my 29th lv
shaman and I wanted to get her to lv 30. I knew that if
I went to highkeep and faught the piclaws I would
get there quickly with little danger. But i decided
to look for bull elefants cause i needed a quest
item off of them and bupped into a creasure called
Tesch Gnolls. Got up to lv 30 in no time at all. I'm
going back there again soon. BTW its located outside of
paw in NK.
